ww.amazon.com/Seagate-Storage-Expansion-Solid-State/dp/B09BJYXMDW/ref=sr_1_3?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;th=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" data-amazonasin=\"B09BJYXMDW\" data-amazontag=\"kinjakotakulink-20\">here</a></span>\n</li>\n<li>Seagate Game Drive for Xbox 2TB - $69.99 (October 10 &amp; 11) - Buy <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\"[]\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Y1Q2KSZ?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" data-amazonasin=\"B08Y1Q2KSZ\" data-amazontag=\"kinjakotakulink-20\">here</a></span>\n</li>\n<li>Seagate Game Drive for Xbox 4TB - $109<!-- -->.99 (October 10 &amp; 11) - Buy <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\"[]\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Y1QRTBM?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" data-amazonasin=\"B08Y1QRTBM\" data-amazontag=\"kinjakotakulink-20\">here</a></span><br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"sc-1bwb26k-1 dezcon\" id=\"h102809\">\n<a class=\"js_header-anchor\" id=\"\"></a>Licensed Nintendo Switch* MicroSD Cards</h2>\n<ul data-type=\"List\" data-style=\"Bullet\" class=\"sc-1lmbno3-0 iPScqk\">\n<li>SanDisk 256GB - $28<!-- -->.99 (October 10 &amp; 11) - Buy <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\"[]\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/SanDisk-256GB-Extreme-UHS-I-Memory/dp/B09X7CFXSX?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulin